Tools To Use Today

Tool / Concept	                    Description
import	                            Import your own Python file (module)
from module import	                Import specific functions from module
.py modules	                        Write and organize code across files
Reuse functions	                    Call pre-written logic cleanly
if __name__ == "__main__"	        Optional: write testable modules


